    "ContentDesc_Windurst: Die dritte Etappe": "Yet another missive from Sareel Ja finds its way into your hands bearing grim tidings. There is to be a coronation for his new king, meaning this may be your last opportunity to thwart his schemes. With Prishe gravely injured, and Bakool Ja Ja assisting the Landsguard, it falls to you and Alxaal to brave the unknown once more. What new dangers await, and what will become of your echo companions should you prove victorious?",
    "ContentName_Windurst: The Third Walk": "Windurst: The Third Walk",
    "Npcyell_13907_Text": "Ugh!",
    "Npcyell_19555_Text": "Shantotto!?",
    "Npcyell_19558_Text": "Reinforcements!",
    "Npcyell_19560_Text": "And now the fight begins in earnest!",
    "Npcyell_19561_Text": "Their leader has finally shown themself.",
    "Npcyell_19562_Text": "It would appear the siege has ended.",
    "Npcyell_19566_Text": "That's the last of them.",
    "Npcyell_19790_Text": "The Galeserpent General's counting on us!",
    "Npcyell_19791_Text": "Damned beastmen!",
    "Npcyell_19795_Text": "Time to get to work!",
    "Npcyell_19814_Text": "Is everyone all right?",
    "Npcyell_19816_Text": "Phew! Glad that's over!",
    "Npcyell_19817_Text": "Time to get our reward!",
    "Npcyell_19818_Text": "Everyone all right? Then let's go eat!",
